high_descs: Turn left then head towards the table, then right towards the sink.
Pick up the knife on the left side of the sink.
Turn around then head towards the table.
Slice the loaf of bread on the table.
Turn right then head towards the sink, then right then head towards the garbage can.
Place the knife into the garbage can.
Turn right then head towards the table.
Pick up a slice of bread from the table.
Turn right then head towards the sink, turn left then head towards the microwave.
Place the slice of bread into the microwave then turn it on.
Remove the slice of bread from the microwave then close the door, turn around then head left towards the garbage can.
Place the slice of bread into the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Place a knife and a slice of microwaved bread into the garbage can.

high_descs: Turn left and move to the sink
Take the knife from the sink
Turn around and move to the table on the right
Cut the bread on the table
Turn around and move to the trash on the right
Put the knife in the trash
Turn around and move to the table on the right
Grab a piece of bread from the table
Turn around to the microwave on the left
Microwave the slice of bread
Take the bread and turn around and move to the trash on the right
Put the bread in the trash
anns.task_desc: Slice a piece of bread and cook it then put it in the trash

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink on the right.
Take the knife out of the sink.
Turn around and approach the bread on the right.
Slice the bread on the table.
Turn around and walk to the trash can.
Put the knife in the trash.
Turn right and walk back to the bread.
Take a slice of bread from the table.
Turn right, then left where the microwave is on the right.
Open the microwave door, put the bread inside, close the door, and turn it on. Remove it when it's done and close the door.
Turn around and walk back to the trash can.
Put the bread in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of bread in the trash.
